Czech Lawmakers May Pass Bill to Limit Commercials, HN Says

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-07-13T06:12:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/czech-lawmakers-may-pass-bill-to-limit-commercials-hn-says.html
Czech lawmakers may pass a bill
today to restrict the broadcasting of commercials on state-owned
television station Ceska Televize,  Hospodarske Noviny  reported.  The bill, if passed, would eliminate commercials from the
CT1 and CT24 channels as of January, restricting them to the CT2
and CT4 channels, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story: Lenka Ponikelska in
Prague   lponikelska1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net ; 